# Interactive Content [box]

## Reveal Block [box]

| reveal Click to see the answer
The hidden answer is revealed when you click!
This is useful for quizzes and self-study materials.

## Reveal with Default Text [box]

| reveal
When no argument is provided, "Click to reveal" is used.


