# Special Blocks [box]

## Contents Block [box]

The `| contents` block generates a table of contents
(processed separately by Render.TOC).

## Endnotes Block [box]

The `| endnotes` block collects and displays all footnotes
from `[footnote ...]` expressions in the document.

## Comment Block [box]

| comment
This text will not appear in the rendered output.
Use comments for notes to yourself or other authors.

The `hide` block works the same as `comment`:

| hide
This is also hidden.

