# Summary [box]

This document demonstrated the following ordinary block types:

**Document Metadata:** `title`, `subtitle`, `author`, `date`, `abstract`

**Headings:** `section` (with level), `subsection`, `subsubsection`,
`section*` (with level arg), `chapter`, `subheading`/`sh`

**Lists:** `- ` items → `itemList`, `. ` items → `numberedList`

**Theorem-like:** `theorem`, `lemma`, `proposition`, `corollary`,
`definition`, `example`, `remark`, `note`, `exercise`, `problem`,
`question`, `axiom` (all with optional label argument), `proof`

**Formatting:** `indent`, `quotation`/`quote`, `center`, `box`,
`compact`, `identity`, `red`, `red2`, `blue`

**Q&A:** `q`, `a`, `reveal` (with optional summary argument)

**Tables/Lists:** `table` (with `format`, `columnWidths`), `desc` (with term)

**Special:** `contents`, `index`, `endnotes`, `comment`/`hide`,
`visibleBanner`, `bibitem` (with key), `env` (with name)

**Configuration (hidden):** `document`, `collection`, `book`, `banner`,
`runninghead_`, `tags`, `type`, `setcounter`, `shiftandsetcounter`
